The paper discusses privacy in voting mechanisms, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of differential privacy techniques and the study of privacy in data release also suggest that the paper could belong to the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
